1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,500
I went on a trip to India

2
00:00:02,609 --> 00:00:05,107
The friend I work with there

3
00:00:05,902 --> 00:00:08,403
brought me sacks full of passports

4
00:00:09,490 --> 00:00:10,391
actual sacks

5
00:00:10,987 --> 00:00:12,987
with several thousand passports

6
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,900
that he placed before me

7
00:00:18,890 --> 00:00:21,588
Certainly it was about who paid him most

8
00:00:21,957 --> 00:00:23,757
He’d come to the office in the morning

9
00:00:25,184 --> 00:00:27,684
he had ash or drawings here

10
00:00:27,832 --> 00:00:31,332
related to his religion

11
00:00:31,893 --> 00:00:33,893
He’d be painted orange here

12
00:00:34,164 --> 00:00:35,362
with a thing on his head

13
00:00:35,651 --> 00:00:36,850
and take a seat

14
00:00:36,972 --> 00:00:38,972
And the people who’d come see him

15
00:00:39,030 --> 00:00:40,530
would trust him more

16
00:00:40,728 --> 00:00:45,030
Like a Hajj here, who has a beard, prays

17
00:00:46,015 --> 00:00:48,015
he took advantage of this in his work

18
00:00:50,941 --> 00:00:52,941
So… he was quite ruthless

19
00:00:53,789 --> 00:00:56,289
If a girl came to him wanting to travel today

20
00:00:56,917 --> 00:00:58,917
and paid more than the girl

21
00:00:59,283 --> 00:01:01,283
already waiting 20 days

22
00:01:01,831 --> 00:01:03,631
she’d travel immediately

23
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:06,319
So we’d match up the girls…

24
00:01:06,694 --> 00:01:09,694
this one with that person

25
00:01:10,128 --> 00:01:13,128
this same one with someone else

26
00:01:13,575 --> 00:01:14,575
They were all here

27
00:01:14,718 --> 00:01:17,718
but each using another woman’s passport

28
00:01:18,483 --> 00:01:21,784
So that the one who paid most, traveled first

29
00:01:22,287 --> 00:01:24,287
And he had connections…

30
00:01:25,019 --> 00:01:29,019
connections there at general security, the airport

31
00:01:30,075 --> 00:01:34,075
everywhere related to the authorities

32
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:36,046
And he didn’t care

33
00:01:36,575 --> 00:01:38,048
so long as he got paid

